## 8. アイコン実装の詳細

### Lucideアイコン（SVG直接記述）

**play（再生）:**
```html
<svg width="9" height="9" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
  <polygon points="5 3 19 12 5 21 5 3" fill="#FFFFFF"/>
</svg>
```

**eye（目）:**
```html
<svg width="9" height="9" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
  <path d="M1 12s4-8 11-8 11 8 11 8-4 8-11 8-11-8-11-8z" stroke="#6B6B6B" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
  <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3" stroke="#6B6B6B" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
</svg>
```

**thumbs-up（いいね）:**
```html
<svg width="9" height="9" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
